Interface ToFileModelTransformable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ClassificationModel, FileLocationModel, HardcodedIPLocationModel, InlineHintModel, JavaAnnotationTypeReferenceModel, JavaTypeReferenceModel, XmlTypeReferenceModel

    public interface ToFileModelTransformable
    An interface to reflect an ability of an model to be transformed to FileModel.
